metadata.name: Beyond the time
metadata.description:
I've always been fascinated by nature and the implicit messages it seems to give.

As in this case, in the Torre Guaceto nature reserve, where this cliff seems to scream to the four winds, that whatever hits it, wind, storms, she will be there, ready to face everything, as if it were beyond time. 

Edition 1/1 

6570x4402 

300 dpi
